Its a remake of the famous fy_iceworld. I completly rebuilt and redesigned it.
It has nice graphics and the gameplay feels very smooth. I tried to balance this small map as good as possible.
I recommend you to play it at 4 vs. 4 but it supports up to 6 vs. 6 matches!
